title: ’Independence is not a final destination’ | I am Catalan
description:
Catalonian identity is about more than a yes or no vote. While the north-eastern Spanish region prepares for the potential declaration of independence, many of the 7 million-strong Catalonian population worry that mainstream media are not representing their voice. We went to Catalonia to ask a variety of people about their identity and what independence means for them.

title: ’Independence is not a final destination’ | I am Catalan
description:
Catalonian identity is about more than a yes or no vote. While the north-eastern Spanish region prepares for the potential declaration of independence, many of the 7 million-strong Catalonian population worry that mainstream media are not representing their voice. We went to Catalonia to ask a variety of people about their identity and what independence means for them.
